CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 12, 1965, pg. 15, reads: "KEY PARTICIPANTS AT CENTRAL WOMEN'S DAY - The success of the recent Women's Day observance at Central Baptist Church... A full day of activity included the afternoon service, which presented Mrs. W. D. Petett as speaker. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Men and women standing in pews and on balcony, with man standing at podium, in Central Baptist Church, possibly for Women's Day
